## ⚙️ System Architecture

Agora connects cognitive orchestration with memory-safe solvers, real-time edge execution, and formal verifiers:

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Agora["🏛️ Scientific Agora — Dialectical Orchestration"]
        direction TB
        Socrates["🧠 Socrates Agent<br/>Philosophical Orchestrator"]
        
        subgraph Hemispheres["Cognitive Pentad (AGY SDK)"]
            Galois["📐 Galois Agent<br/>Creative Mathematician<br/>(SymBrain v4 Cortex)"]
            Galileo["🔭 Galileo Agent<br/>Empirical Experimenter<br/>(SUNDIALS Solvers)"]
            Euler["📐 Euler Agent<br/>Skeptical Verifier<br/>(Leanabell Prover V2)"]
        end
 
        Socrates -->|"1. Inquire & Direct"| Galois
        Galois -->|"2. Conjectures & Sketches"| Galileo
        Galileo -->|"3. Numerical & Physical Data"| Euler
        Euler -->|"4. Logical Audits & Proofs"| Socrates
        Socrates -->|"5. Philosophical Feedback"| Galois
    end

    subgraph Storage["📂 Vault & Memory Catalog"]
