## 📦 Codebase Directory & Directory Links

Below is the directory mapping of the SocrateAI Scientific Agora repository. Explore individual modules directly:

*   **[`core/`](core/)**: Rust implementation of the **SymBrain v5** core.
    *   [`core/src/symbrain/`](core/src/symbrain/): Prefrontal Cortex (PFC) router, RLCF curvature-aware optimizer, dynamic gating, early stopping, and INT8 co-processor pipeline.
    *   [`core/src/memory/`](core/src/memory/): Pre-allocated memory arena, bump allocators, and NUMA-aware allocation.
    *   [`core/src/kernel/`](core/src/kernel/): Simd tensor engines, task schedulers, and FFI mappings.
*   **[`solvers/`](solvers/)**: Rust bindings and physics solvers.
    *   [`solvers/src/sundials/`](solvers/src/sundials/): CVODE implicit solver bridges, stiff kinetics (Robertson), Lorenz attractors, predator-prey dynamics, and steady 2D Navier-Stokes.
    *   [`solvers/src/physics/`](solvers/src/physics/): Invariant checking routines (mass, charge, energy, boundary conditions).
*   **[`agents/`](agents/)**: Multi-agent Python SDK framework.
    *   [`agents/base.py`](agents/base.py): Base AbstractAgent implementation.
    *   [`agents/socrates/`](agents/socrates/): Dialectical orchestrator and Elenchus-Maieutic logic loops.
    *   [`agents/galois/`](agents/galois/): Out-of-the-box mathematical conics generator.
    *   [`agents/galileo/`](agents/galileo/): SUNDIALS simulator and empirical investigator.
    *   [`agents/euler/`](agents/euler/): Proof-verifier, auditor, and DeepProbLog logic parser.
    *   [`agents/turing/`](agents/turing/): Computer science profiler and dynamic parameters optimizer.
    *   [`agents/hypatie/`](agents/hypatie/): Astronomical archivist and astrolabe conics cataloger.
*   **[`verifiers/`](verifiers/)**: Strict logical and mathematical formal checking engines.
    *   [`verifiers/lean4/Agora/`](verifiers/lean4/Agora/): Axiomatized proofs in Lean 4 (LoRA norm bounds, RLCF descent Lyapunov convergence, arena boundaries, and boundary conservation).
    *   [`verifiers/deepproblog/`](verifiers/deepproblog/): DeepProbLog neural predicates, type-constraint Prolog programs, and skeptical step-by-step audits.
*   **[`alexandrie/`](alexandrie/)**: Hugging Face-style scientific hub FastAPI backend for artifact vaults.
*   **[`deploy/`](deploy/)**: Cost-optimized serverless GCP configuration files.
    *   [`deploy/terraform/`](deploy/terraform/): Scalable GCP Terraform modules featuring automatic cost ceilings and `min_replicas = 0` Cloud Run.
    *   [`deploy/docker/`](deploy/docker/): Optimized Dockerfiles for agents, servers, and solvers.
*   **[`nvidia/`](nvidia/)**: Direct integration points to Nvidia microservices.
    *   [`nvidia/bionemo/`](nvidia/bionemo/): ESM2 protein structure solvers and sequence validators.
    *   [`nvidia/earth2/`](nvidia/earth2/): Weather and climate forecasters.
    *   [`nvidia/modulus/`](nvidia/modulus/): Physics-informed neural network (PINN) solvers.
*   **[`benchmarks/`](benchmarks/)**: Evaluation harnesses for GSM8K, MATH, and Physics.
*   **[`examples/`](examples/)**: Step-by-step code demonstrations.
    *   [`examples/stiff_ode_solver.py`](examples/stiff_ode_solver.py): Stiff chemical kinetics.
    *   [`examples/dialectic_reasoning.py`](examples/dialectic_reasoning.py): Galileo-Euler Socratic debate.

